input: 12:30 - What's written as "(1 + r)" should really just be r, by any usual convention for how to write an interest rate.
translatedText: 12:30 - Ang isinulat bilang "(1 + r)" ay dapat talagang r, sa pamamagitan ng anumang karaniwang kombensiyon kung paano magsulat ng rate ng interes.
